"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-00435258-57b1-49a3-b10a-b4a54f780cb7\">지하철 7호선 남성역 1번출구 앞,  이수한의원</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-bdda233b-21a3-4825-b058-d13a0c9c1497\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-106571e9-0c1e-4570-b0f0-b8307a586330\">예약 문의 02-584-1075 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-e811f597-f543-4cb4-8da0-7c3d1566d8bc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4ab75694-685a-40dd-94cb-441a4989dbf0\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-e9e13344-25ef-4094-9488-a856a6f4427c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3ba7617c-1388-43e3-ac9f-ad606d953c50\">네이버 예약 링크</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:2.0;\" id=\"SE-09118997-d952-40e1-93e0-6bb464590f16\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-373f03b7-575d-4c4f-838d-bbbe8aaa2712\"><a href=\"https://booking.naver.com/booking/13/bizes/331349?tr&#x3D;bnm\" class=\"se-link\" target=\"_blank\">https://booking.naver.com/booking/13/bizes/331349?tr&#x3D;bnm</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-large_image\" id=\"SE-cef82d6d-d2b0-41e0-b932-76f4bed94c03\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-oglink se-l-large_image se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-oglink\">\n                                <a href=\"https://booking.naver.com/booking/13/biz